Thugs break into missing Lawyer Simon Lilan&#39;s office in Eldoret and make away with computers and other documents.Mr. Lilan had filed a suit to block the burial of former nominated MP Mark Too who died on December 31 last year at St Luke Hospital in Eldoret. The missing Lawyer was last seen on 9th January 2016 and his family who were concerned about his safety reported the case to the police.LSK President Isaac Okero had probed the police to investigate and locate the missing lawyer Simon Lilan. ALSO READ: Couple facing murder charge now set free